title: Flight Simulator 2020 - World Update III - Bristol
description:
In this video we will look at the Bristol which is part of World Update III: UK & Ireland which has been released today. We are taking of from Bristol airport and are flying via Cardiff to Oxford. During our flight we will see several POI's which have been added in the surroundings of Cardiff and Oxford.
